                  "typeName": "dsDescriptionValue",
                  "typeClass": "primitive",
                  "multiple": false,
                  "value": "A tidy, documented, reproducible dataset of Colorado reservoir storage (volume, pool elevation, and releases), liberated from public APIs (Colorado DWR/CDSS and USBR Reclamation RISE) into a single long-format CSV: one row per (source, reservoir_id, datetime, variable). Part of the Colorado Environmental Data Hub (CUPIDS Lab); implements issue #9. Each extract carries per-source provenance (source URL, retrieval time, SHA-256, license). Regenerated and re-audited monthly from the source APIs; see the repository for the re-runnable pipeline."
                }
